    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks like it literally just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve kept it in pristine shape\u2014not a single scratch or smudge anywhere. It drives like a dream and still has that wonderful new-car smell. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one! I'm so excited for someone new to get behind the wheel and enjoy it as much as I have. Let's get you in for a test drive!",
