    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in impeccable condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through a Getrag six-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS unit has been professionally bulletproofed, and the rear subframe has been reinforced with Turner Motorsport plates to ensure long-term structural integrity. The suspension retains its precise factory geometry with refreshed bushings and OEM dampers. Finished in Laguna Seca Blue, the exterior exhibits zero oxidation or swirling, while the undercarriage remains free of corrosion. A turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
