      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. The exterior is finished in a deep, lustrous coat with a professional-grade ceramic sealant, showing zero rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats are supple with no bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or rattles. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been strictly garage-kept and maintained with an open-checkbook policy at authorized service centers\u2014full records included. Every button functions as intended, the engine pulls smoothly across the rev range, and the transmission shifts with factory crispness. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously preserved example of automotive excellence.",
